show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: A seemingly jobless and meek Aarav endures daily humiliation from his in-laws, while his wife Priya struggles to shield him from their scorn. But when Aarav’s hidden identity as the powerful heir of the Mittal empire is revealed, their world turns upside down love, loyalty, and revenge collide in this tale of masks, marriage, and shocking revelations. Watch Now!
